variables.name: frames
variables.comment: The window frames used by the client side for layout.

variables.name: mergedConfiguration
variables.comment:
* New config container that holds global, override and merged config for window, if it is now
     * becoming visible and the merged config has changed since it was last displayed.

variables.name: surfaceControl
variables.comment: Object in which is placed the new display surface.

variables.name: insetsState
variables.comment: The current insets state in the system.

variables.name: syncSeqId
variables.comment: The latest sync seq id for the relayout configuration.

variables.name: activityWindowInfo
variables.comment:
* The latest {@link ActivityWindowInfo} if this relayout window is an Activity window.
     * {@code null} if this is not an Activity window.
